    <p class="hero-sub">Tap into India's emerging growth companies ranked beyond 250 by market cap. Small cap funds offer the highest return potential among equity categories, ideal for aggressive investors with a 7+ year horizon willing to embrace volatility for exceptional wealth creation.</p>
